Definition at line 93 of file isabRouteList.h.

void IsabRouteList::perturbLastWptToAvoidDivideByZero (   )  [private]
 

Workaround for old clients that uses an unsafe method to calculate the angle between any waypoint and the end point.

This method will perturb the coordinate of the last waypoint (since this one is the most likely to have the same coordinate as the endpoint) in case it has the same coordinate as the endpoint.
